          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1626176902606-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a splash of<strong> water</strong> and cook, covered, for 2 min or until completely wilted, then stir in the <strong>drained noodles </strong>and<strong> toasted sesame oil</strong> – these are your <strong>sesame noodles</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1626176910597-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1626176910597-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1626176910597-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1626176910597-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1626176910597-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>hoisin mushrooms</strong> over the<strong> sesame noodles</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
